{"tid":1723461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旭日行動後續檢討","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:01:04.000Z","uid":266672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8ca067efe12b6419daa255fededeb24d8bb713","tid":1723461,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"睇下之前星期二個陣<br />\n<br />\n冇晒巴士 黨鐵又冇一堆 巴士又做埋rb<br />\n<br />\n跟住通街都係磚 rb <br />\n連帶影響埋星期三<br />\n<br />\n真係行路番工都唔掂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依家開始成果冇咁大 <br />\n最主要係學生放假就真係放假<br />\n巴士又慢慢開番晒<br />\n同埋又多左藍絲落場 之前辛辛苦苦起既rb.. <br />\n<br />\n大家傾下可以點樣繼續黎明行動啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要班學生日日停課 佢地可能會一齊落場幫手"},{"pid":"02be7d2ebfd3fec94b5750cf3a5b7b8dd41de493","tid":1723461,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"無人呀屌你老母<br />\n當銀髮係condom??<br />\n<br />\n下午四點，中環遮打銀髮要人，想多謝銀髮就入黎推，同埋晏d 加入（有不反）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723219</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66aeaaa8734d789a5d683c85925321fecb4401fc","tid":1723461,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"九龍區好成功喎<br />\n今日晨早要去中環搞D野,順便幫手迫下地鐵<br />\n好多人習慣左 已經冇人屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迫左個幾鐘先過到海<br />\n<br />\n12點左右係中環坐小輪去尖咀諗住搭巴士<br />\n仆你個街, 碼頭巴士站一架巴士都冇<br />\n行出D 成個尖咀都見唔到巴士同小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得D 貨VAN,的士同私家車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九龍區塞得好撚有效架 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5214a105eca04ffb24768dd8418d4ee3ef4d32fb","tid":1723461,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"最懷情況就係愈黎愈少人 然後慢慢收皮<br />\n配合得個行動既都係學生/罷工仔 罷一星期其實好極限<br />\n當然你可以要求人繼續罷工 但人數突減既話唔好屌晒鬼<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動個人覺得係證明左另一種抗爭方法係work<br />\n但門檻極高 唔係辭左職個班好難同你長期作戰 <br />\n至於普通中學生 有參加琴日同今日行動就知有無效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d168ca56b3d52149e86f39bcc756769121444c6e","tid":1723461,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"中環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a859e2557fdd24c7bfb6d1e137561d9312ee8e97","tid":1723461,"uid":82090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"你罷人時同時比人罷<br />\n咁既話每日都可以去塞 就算唔罷都要塞車遲返 對公司實有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35fb3ab71a052ecee3edecdab2cf87cfffa3e13","tid":1723461,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴士係我哋最強嘅護盾</span>"},{"pid":"422d44a2dced255433c4f2de321c8de85a0a5818","tid":1723461,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"破中共陽謀，和理非最終升級：<span style=\"color: red;\">「和理掃」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723558/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723558/</a>"},{"pid":"d3025121d8fbc4debfce2236c7fba5a2fe1b3da9","tid":1723461,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5214a105eca04ffb24768dd8418d4ee3ef4d32fb","tid":1723461,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"最懷情況就係愈黎愈少人 然後慢慢收皮<br />\n配合得個行動既都係學生/罷工仔 罷一星期其實好極限<br />\n當然你可以要求人繼續罷工 但人數突減既話唔好屌晒鬼<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動個人覺得係證明左另一種抗爭方法係work<br />